@node "Script" "Script         "
@{fg shine}The Script Editor@{fg text}

At Last!!  You can now put together all the elements of your adventure and
take it for a test drive!  The Engine requires a completely full script in
order to work properly, so @{u}you MUST have all the following filled in@{uu}:

@{i}  Opening IFF Image
  Description Backround IFF Image
  Description @{b}@{ui}ASCII@{i}@{ub} Text File (up to 24 lines long)
  .CMAP File
  .COBJ File
  .OLCT File
  .CANM File
  Sound/Noise/ProTracker Module (played with those wonderful
                                 Amos Track Commands!!)
  Closing IFF Image@{ui}

One missing file, and KAPUT!  There goes the Engine!

@{fg shine}Disk--@{fg text}

Save your Script File (its in @{b}Ascii@{ub}...open it up and figure our how its put
together!)

